          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1613556895300-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>In a separate large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick), heat a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped garlic, blanched peas </strong>and <strong>sliced spring greens </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 4 min or until cooked with a slight bite – these are your <strong>garlicky greens</strong></p>",
